91)\n* '''[[Roy Reding]]''' ([[Circonscription Centre (Luxembourg)|Centre]]: 2013\u2013present)\n* '''[[Jeff Engelen]]''' ([[Circonscription Nord (Luxembourg)|Nord]]: 2018-)\n{{Col-end}}\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|conservatism}}\n* [[List of political parties in Luxembourg]]\n\n==Footnotes==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==References==\n*{{cite interview |last=Camus |first=Jean-Yves |subject-link= |interviewer=Christoph Bumb & Pol Schock |title= Extremism-researcher Camus: \"The ADR is not right-wing populist |url=https://www.wort.lu/de/politik/extremismusforscher-jean-yves-camus-die-adr-ist-nicht-rechtspopulistisch-588e44c7a5e74263e13a9c53 |publisher= |location= |date= |work= |access-date=}}\n* {{cite journal |last1=Dumont |first1=Patrick |last2=Fehlen |first2=Fernand |last3=Kies |first3=Rapha\u00ebl |last4=Poirier |first4=Philippe |year=2006 |title=Les \u00e9lections l\u00e9gislatives et europ\u00e9ennes de 2004 au Grand-Duch\u00e9 de Luxembourg |publisher=[[Chamber of Deputies of Luxembourg|Chamber of Deputies]] |url=http://www.chd.lu/wps/wcm/connect/57c4e7804e295e05b6adf7010df100bc/Rapport_complet_elections2004.pdf?MOD=AJPERES |language=fr}}\n* {{cite book |title=The Handbook of West European Pension Politics |last=Immergut |first=Ellen M. |author2=Anderson, Karen M.|author3= Schulze, Isabelle |year=2007 |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=Oxford |isbn=978-0-19-929147-2 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=T0pYjE6REq4C }}\n* {{cite book |title=Campaigning in Europe - Campaigning for Europe |last=Maier |first=Michaela |author2=Tenscher, Jens |year=2004 |publisher=LIT Verlag M\u00fcnster |location=M\u00fcnster |isbn=978-3-8258-9322-4 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=j9NjsybIcgoC }}\n* {{cite book |title=Christian Democratic Parties in Europe Since the End of the Cold War |last=Van Hecke |first=Steven |author2=Gerard, Emmanuel |year=2004 |publisher=Leuven University Press |location=Leuven |isbn=978-90-5867-377-0 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QJ6x8zmRAaEC